### ============================================================
### IDTSignatureController - API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-plans/{carePlanId}/idt-signatures
### sc-036 - IDT Acknowledgment
### ============================================================

### [1] GET IDT signatures - care plan có signatures
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-plans/1/idt-signatures
X-User-Role: DON

###

### [2] GET IDT signatures - as ADMIN
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-plans/1/idt-signatures
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### [3] GET IDT signatures - care plan chưa có ai ký
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-plans/2/idt-signatures
X-User-Role: DON

###

### [4] GET IDT signatures - care plan not found
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-plans/9999/idt-signatures
X-User-Role: DON

###

### [5] POST submit IDT signature - PHYSICIAN ký, có comments
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-plans/1/idt-signatures
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Role: PHYSICIAN

{
  "userId": 1,
  "comments": "Reviewed and acknowledged. Care plan aligns with medical orders."
}

###

### [6] POST submit IDT signature - DIETITIAN ký, có comments
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-plans/1/idt-signatures
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Role: DIETITIAN

{
  "userId": 2,
  "comments": "Nutritional goals reviewed. Diet plan consistent with care plan."
}

###

### [7] POST submit IDT signature - không có comments (null)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-plans/1/idt-signatures
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Role: PHYSICIAN

{
  "userId": 3,
  "comments": null
}

###

### [8] POST submit IDT signature - care plan khác
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-plans/2/idt-signatures
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Role: PHYSICIAN

{
  "userId": 1,
  "comments": "Acknowledged for care plan 2."
}

###

### [9] POST submit IDT signature - duplicate (user đã ký rồi -> 409 CONFLICT)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-plans/1/idt-signatures
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Role: PHYSICIAN

{
  "userId": 1,
  "comments": "Trying to sign again"
}

###

### [10] POST submit IDT signature - user not found
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-plans/1/idt-signatures
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Role: PHYSICIAN

{
  "userId": 9999,
  "comments": "Test with invalid user"
}

###

### [11] POST submit IDT signature - care plan not found
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-plans/9999/idt-signatures
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Role: DIETITIAN

{
  "userId": 1,
  "comments": "Test with invalid care plan"
}

###

### [12] FORBIDDEN - NURSE không được GET (chỉ DON/ADMIN)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-plans/1/idt-signatures
X-User-Role: NURSE

###

### [13] FORBIDDEN - DON không được POST (chỉ PHYSICIAN/DIETITIAN)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-plans/1/idt-signatures
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Role: DON

{
  "userId": 1,
  "comments": "DON trying to sign"
}

###

### [14] FORBIDDEN - CNA không được POST
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-plans/1/idt-signatures
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Role: CNA

{
  "userId": 1,
  "comments": "CNA trying to sign"
}

###

### [15] UNAUTHORIZED - không có role header (GET)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-plans/1/idt-signatures

###

### [16] UNAUTHORIZED - không có role header (POST)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-plans/1/idt-signatures
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "comments": "No auth header"
}

###
